OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1773191770
OL,3,CEx-partner tells court Natalie McNally
OL,4,Cdeath unrelated to phone reset
OL,6,FAn ex-partner of murder victim Natalie
OL,7,FMcNally has said resetting his phone
OL,8,Fafter her death had been nothing to do
OL,9,Fwith her.
OL,11,FThe man, who cannot be named because
OL,12,Fof a court order, had been arrested
OL,13,Ffor questioning by detectives probing
OL,14,Fthe murder but was later released.
OL,16,FNatalie McNally, 32, was 15 weeks
OL,17,Fpregnant when she was killed at her
OL,18,Fhome in Lurgan on December 18 2022.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/10
