PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1773191770
OL,3,CEx-partner tells court Natalie McNally
OL,4,Cdeath unrelated to phone reset
OL,6,FOn Monday, the court heard that the
OL,7,Fman had been watching the World Cup
OL,8,Ffinal with his then partner on the
OL,9,Fnight that Ms McNally was killed, and
OL,10,Fthat his then partner had a video of
OL,11,Fhim on that night asleep on the sofa.
OL,13,FHe said he first learned Ms McNally
OL,14,Fwas dead after one of her neighbours
OL,15,Fcontacted him on the Snapchat app to
OL,16,Ftell him.
OL,18,F"She said she's been murdered, I think
OL,19,Fshe said Natalie has been stabbed at
OL,20,Fthe top of her stairs," he said.
OL,26,@zD@AOU|D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
