PN,44606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1773191770
OL,3,CEx-partner tells court Natalie McNally
OL,4,Cdeath unrelated to phone reset
OL,6,FHe also said he thought the killing
OL,7,Fmight have been accidental, or that
OL,8,Fshe might have miscarried and taken
OL,9,Fher own life after some negative
OL,10,Fmessaging between them recently.
OL,12,FHe was also told by his then partner
OL,13,Fthat police had been to the house to
OL,14,Fspeak to him about Ms McNally while he
OL,15,Fhad been at work.
OL,17,FDefence barrister John Kearney KC
OL,18,Fasked him about how he had factory
OL,19,Freset his mobile phone days after her
OL,20,Fmurder.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1773191770
OL,3,CEx-partner tells court Natalie McNally
OL,4,Cdeath unrelated to phone reset
OL,6,FThe man said that had been nothing to
OL,7,Fdo with Ms McNally's murder.
OL,9,FHe said he did it before he spoke to
OL,10,Fpolice because he was concerned about
OL,11,Fdrugs he had in his house.
OL,13,F"I factory reset it for a reason... it
OL,14,Fhad nothing to do with deleting
OL,15,Fmessages between me and Natalie."
OL,17,FHe described having two detectives
OL,18,Fsitting in his flat while he had a
OL,19,F"big bag of weed" in a cupboard.
OL,26,@uD@AOUwD@aO]{D@AOU{D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1773191770
OL,3,CEx-partner tells court Natalie McNally
OL,4,Cdeath unrelated to phone reset
OL,6,F"It was because there would have been
OL,7,Fmessages to do with drugs, and weed in
OL,8,Fparticular," he said.
OL,10,FAsked why he had not just deleted
OL,11,Fthose particular messages, he
OL,12,Fresponded: "My best friend had just
OL,13,Fbeen murdered, detectives were in my
OL,14,Fhouse, I wanted to get there quick, I
OL,15,Ffactory reset the phone because I had
OL,16,Fa feeling they're going to smell the
OL,17,Fweed.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@LO]tD@LOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1773191770
OL,3,CEx-partner tells court Natalie McNally
OL,4,Cdeath unrelated to phone reset
OL,6,F"That didn't happen, in hindsight I
OL,7,Fdidn't need to do that and I shouldn't
OL,8,Fhave done it, but I was worried they
OL,9,Fwere going to want my phone."
OL,11,FMr Kearney also asked if he had told
OL,12,FNatalie's neighbour that there had
OL,13,Fbeen some "nasty" messaging between
OL,14,FMcNally and himself.
OL,16,FHe responded: "I was probably telling
OL,17,Fher everything, the truth, I had been
OL,18,Fsending nasty messages, dirty
OL,19,Fmessages, whatever."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@]O]uD@KOUuD@QO]xD@OOU{D@TO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/10
