OL,3,CEx-partner tells court Natalie McNally
OL,4,Cdeath unrelated to phone reset
OL,6,FThe man also described being almost
OL,7,Feight weeks sober and being involved
OL,8,Fwith a new partner.
OL,10,FThe trial continues.
